{{Top|leg|canon=Plastcrete}}
'''Plasticrete''', also spelled '''plastcrete''', was a building material used in cheap [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] constructs.<ref name="Entanglements">{{WEGCite|story=To Hunt the Hutt|book=Imperial Entanglements (Star Wars Miniatures Battles)}}</ref> It was also used as a layering for corridors in [[Byrne City]] carved from the bedrock on the planet [[Demophon]].<ref name="SN">[[Supernova (sourcebook)|''Supernova'']]</ref>

